snippet.title: Volcano Princess Announcement Trailer | TGS 2022
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1669980/Volcano_Princess/

You and your daughter live in the Volcano Kingdom. While raising your daughter, the conflict between humans and demons is intensifying. What kind of person will she grow up to be? Every decision you make will affect the future of your daughter, and even the Volcano Kingdom.

Demo coming to Steam in October.
